This is Simple Blog Application with subdomain concept
Steps to be followed
1) Edit database.yml
2) rake db:create
3) rake db:migrate
4) rake db:seed
5)edit /etc/hosts/ add blog.local account1.blog.local railspress.blog.local
6)script/server
7)http://blog.local:3000/
8)railspress.blog.local/login
  username=admin
  password=Admin123!
9)Create new Account
  account1 => subdomain  
Still This application is in Development Mode
